<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Walther von Seckendorff zu Stopfenheim</head><p>Der Rat bittet erneut, den Kaspar Wernitzer, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen seines Guts nicht zu belästigen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_267" id="133r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_267_r1l12"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Walthern von Seckendorff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l13">cʒu Stoppfenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_267_r1l14">Lıeber her walther / Als wir ewch vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haben von Caſpar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l15">wernicʒers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers vnd ſeins guts vvegen / daran Jr Jn irret vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l16">enget / Alſo iſt derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> aber für vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd hat vns <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l17">vvie Jr Jn noch daran hindert / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jn durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l18"><expan>vngehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vnd vngeenget laſſen wöllet / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l19">vnd biten des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gütlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_267" id="133r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Walthern von Seckendorff czu Stoppfenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Walther, als wir ewch vormals
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haben von Caspar
                        Werniczers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers, und seins guts wegen,
                        daran ir in irret und enget, also ist derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> aber für uns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und hat uns <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>, wie ir in noch daran hindert.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> und
                        ungeenget lassen wöllet. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        Und biten des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gütlich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
